## CULTURAL REQUIREMENTS

```
ENABLERS:
  - Blameless postmortems (Σ < 0 is learning, not failure)
  - Psychological safety (surface tension early)
  - DevOps maturity (automation for gates)
  - Leadership alignment (KPIs on Σ health, not just velocity)

BLOCKERS:
  - Siloed teams (κ accounting disputes)
  - Bonus-driven metric gaming (Σ as vanity number)
  - Fear of Σ < 0 blame (hide problems instead)
  - Velocity-only culture (gas pedal, no chassis)

ADOPTION PATH:
  1. Start with single team/project
  2. Automate κ tracking in PR template
  3. Add Σ state (GREEN/YELLOW/RED) to CI
  4. Scale after wins
  5. Never full-framework-upfront
```

